OL,3,CStokie Rob keeps record of every pub
OL,4,Che goes in - now he's visited his
OL,5,C12,000th
OL,7,FAle-loving Rob Cocker has just sunk a
OL,8,Fpint in his 12,000th pub - having kept
OL,9,Fa record of every boozer he's visited
OL,10,Fover the last 55 years.
OL,12,FThe 73-year-old, of Penkhull, has
OL,13,Fdrank in all 55 English cities during
OL,14,Fthat time as well as frequenting every
OL,15,Fsingle alehouse within 20 minutes of
OL,16,Fhis home.
OL,18,FCAMRA member Rob reached his latest
OL,19,Fmilestone on Friday when he took the
OL,20,Ftrain to Warrington for a civilised
OL,21,Fpub crawl.
