OL,3,CStokie Rob keeps record of every pub
OL,4,Che goes in - now he's visited his
OL,5,C12,000th
OL,7,FHe supped his landmark pint in the
OL,8,Fhighly-rated Costello's Bar in nearby
OL,9,FStockton Heath.
OL,11,FRob describes himself as a 'statto'
OL,12,Fand, aged 18, started to write down
OL,13,Fthe names of the pubs he visited on
OL,14,Fthe back of a fag packet before
OL,15,Feventually keeping a diary.
