OL,3,CStokie Rob keeps record of every pub
OL,4,Che goes in - now he's visited his
OL,5,C12,000th
OL,7,FHe told Stoke-on-Trent Live: "I don't
OL,8,Fwant to travel too far these days. I
OL,9,Fchose Warrington because there are a
OL,10,Fcouple of pubs close to the train
OL,11,Fstation and I can get to Stockton
OL,12,FHeath on a bus.
OL,14,F"A couple of the pubs are also in The
OL,15,FGood Beer Guide. I'd say 99 per cent
OL,16,Fof pubs I visit are either in the
OL,17,Fguide or have been, or they sell real
OL,18,Fale."
