OL,3,CStokie Rob keeps record of every pub
OL,4,Che goes in - now he's visited his
OL,5,C12,000th
OL,7,FBack in March 2020, Rob was
OL,8,Fcelebrating visiting his 11,000th
OL,9,Fdifferent pub - but little did he know
OL,10,Fthen that it would take him more than
OL,11,Ffour years to frequent another 1,000.
OL,13,FJust weeks after his feat, the country
OL,14,Fwent into lockdown due to the pandemic.
OL,16,F"It felt like the pubs were shut for
OL,17,Fan eternity," said Rob. "I remember
OL,18,Fgoing back to my local The Marquis
OL,19,Fwhen the ban was lifted and then
OL,20,Feverything shut down again.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
