OL,3,CStokie Rob keeps record of every pub
OL,4,Che goes in - now he's visited his
OL,5,C12,000th
OL,7,F"I also remember going to the
OL,8,FWetherspoon in Hanley and sitting
OL,9,Foutside while it was lashing down."
OL,11,FLast weekend, Rob bought a rail ticket
OL,12,Fwith unlimited travel and stopped off
OL,13,Fat several places - including Derby,
OL,14,FLeicester, Peterborough and Nottingham
OL,15,F- in order to sample new boozers.
OL,17,FAnd he managed to do it all in a day -
OL,18,Fbeing tucked up in bed just after 9pm.
