OL,3,CStokie Rob keeps record of every pub
OL,4,Che goes in - now he's visited his
OL,5,C12,000th
OL,7,F"Since July I've made 14 trips and I
OL,8,Fstop at 10 or 11 pubs each time on
OL,9,Faverage", he said. "Last Saturday I
OL,10,Fgot the East Midlands Day Ranger
OL,11,Fticket and visited 13 pubs.
OL,13,F"I set off on the train at 9.33am and
OL,14,FI was back in the house by 9.10pm. I
OL,15,Fget chatting to shed loads of people.
OL,16,FWhen I tell people I'm approaching my
OL,17,F12,000th pub they say 'get off'.
OL,18,FThey're gobsmacked."
