OL,3,CStokie Rob keeps record of every pub
OL,4,Che goes in - now he's visited his
OL,5,C12,000th
OL,7,FHe added: "I follow Stoke home and
OL,8,Faway so get a lot of pubs in that way.
OL,9,FWe play Sheffield United away soon and
OL,10,Fthere are seven new pubs I'll be
OL,11,Fvisiting in the Woodseats area.
OL,13,F"My wife has been on the pub trips
OL,14,Fwith me too - she's approaching 3,000."
